Class EnergyUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.iceyleagons.frostedengineering.network.energy.EnergyUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Battery, CoalGenerator

    public abstract class EnergyUnit
extends java.lang.Object
implements Unit, java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    TOTHT

    This is the smallest unit of an EnergyNetwork all the components have relations with this superclass (except Transformators, those aren't units)
